 fit in with a band's?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event151-02-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"It may not qualify as... special... but I do make an effort to preserve the atmosphere of the music.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event151-02-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"Doing so requires the creation of an atmosphere that a violin can seamlessly blend into. As for the how, I draw inspiration from classical music.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event151-02-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"Mashiro","body":"(I had no idea Rui-san was thinking about that while writing for us...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"kandou01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"event151-02-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"That's very interesting~. Drawing from classical music is similar to what CHU²-san does.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event151-02-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"CHU²-san?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event151-02-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"She's our producer. She listens to all kinds of music, including classical, when she's composing.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event151-02-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"She's so amazing~. She's younger than us, but she writes lyrics and composes music!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event151-02-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"Mashiro","body":"She writes such incredible music all by herself...? Wow...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"event151-02-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"Also, don't you think it's kind of cool to be called the producer?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"chuni01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event151-02-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"I wish I could say I'm Roselia's producer at least once~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event151-02-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"Mashiro","body":"B-but I think you're already very cool, Ako-chan... You're like the one that guides Roselia's powerful and epic music...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeF